            <li><a href="https://github.com/sun475300-sudo/swarm-drone-atc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
            <li><a href="report/SDACS_Final_Report_v6.docx" download>Report v6</a></li>
            <li><a href="report/SDACS_Final_Report_v7_Easy.docx" download>Report v7</a></li>
            <li><a href="swarm_3d_simulator_v2.html">3D Simulator v2 (신규)</a></li>
            <li><a href="swarm_3d_simulator.html">3D Simulator v1</a></li>
